---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="写作入口" description="Reid's Notes 的共创写作入口。">
  <section class="write-entry section">
    <div class="write-entry__copy">
      <p class="eyebrow">Writing Room</p>
      <h1 class="display-title">一起写。</h1>
      <p class="write-entry__intro article-serif">
        这里是共创入口。登录 GitHub 后，可以直接在浏览器里写文章、上传图片、提交发布。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="write-entry__actions" aria-label="写作入口">
      <a class="write-entry__primary" href="https://github.dev/ZHUCH-520/ZHUCH-520.github.io">
        打开网页编辑器
      </a>
      <a class="write-entry__secondary" href="https://github.com/ZHUCH-520/ZHUCH-520.github.io">
        打开 GitHub 仓库
      </a>
      <a
        class="write-entry__secondary"
        href="https://github.com/ZHUCH-520/ZHUCH-520.github.io/tree/main/templates/post"
      >
        查看文章模板
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="write-entry__notes article-serif">
      <p>新文章放在 <code>src/content/posts/文章-slug/index.mdx</code>，图片放在 <code>public/media/posts/</code>。</p>
      <p>文章可以先保存为草稿；取消草稿后，提交到主分支会自动发布到网站。</p>
      <p>如果后台提示没有权限，需要先接受 GitHub collaborator 邀请，并确认当前账号有仓库写权限。</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .write-entry {
    min-height: calc(100vh - 156px);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(280px, 360px);
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .write-entry__copy {
    display: grid;
    gap: 26px;
  }

  .write-entry__copy .display-title {
    max-width: 620px;
    font-size: clamp(54px, 8vw, 92px);
  }

  .write-entry__intro {
    max-width: 540px;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 23px;
    line-height: 1.85;
  }

  .write-entry__actions {
    display: grid;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .write-entry__actions a {
    min-height: 48px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .write-entry__primary {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper-strong);
  }

  .write-entry__primary:hover {
    color: var(--paper-strong);
  }

  .write-entry__secondary {
    background: rgba(255, 253, 247, 0.48);
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .write-entry__notes {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    max-width: 720px;
    padding-top: 22px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .write-entry__notes p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .write-entry__notes p + p {
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  .write-entry__notes code {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 0.88em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .write-entry {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 34px;
      min-height: auto;
      padding-top: 48px;
    }
  }
</style>
